## 手动配置IP
```sh
# ifconfig - net-tools
$ sudo ifconfig eth1 172.16.36.131/24
$ sudo ifconfig eth1 up

# ip - iproute2
$ sudo ip addr add 172.16.36.131/24 dev eth1
$ sudo ip link set up eth1
```

